[Amit Varma]: Frederick Bastia, who is also the inspiration behind the name of this podcast, the seen

00:41:37.720 --> 00:41:38.880
[Amit Varma]: in the unseen.

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:43.520
[Amit Varma]: And Bastia wrote about just as you were talking about, you know, giving lunch to the people

00:41:43.520 --> 00:41:44.520
[Amit Varma]: of Mumbai.

